Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:19.91,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Je tu niekto, kto nemá žiadne tajomstvá?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:24.04,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Na to, aby som to povedal, sa príliš bojím.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:26.50,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Bojím sa, že sa niečo pokazí,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.02,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,ak to poviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.46,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,Ale naozaj chcem,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.95,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,aby to vedela.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:35.34,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Teraz by mala byť
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.26,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,v triede sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:57.42,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:12.51,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Aj tak nemám
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:15.67,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,čo stratiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:20.94,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Takže choď, Kuromine Asahi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:49.21,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,Titulky od GAW-Subs\Nwww.gawsubs.com
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:14.96,jitsuwa-ep-title,Text,0,0,0,,Vyznám sa jej!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.08,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vyznám sa jej!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.76,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Už nie som ten istý muž ako dakedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.26,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Už ma neprečítate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:25.26,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie, dokiaľ mám tieto moderné okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:37.44,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Takže túto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.10,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Juj!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.15,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.43,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Vždy mám pocit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.53,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,že robím niečo ako svätokrádež, keď s tebou hrám starú pani, Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.46,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.16,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Ty si taký deravý kôš, Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.81,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,"Deravý kôš" ani nedáva zmysel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:54.04,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Koše majú byť deravé!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.30,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Nah,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.96,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,ty si deravý kôš, pretože máš v sebe ešte viac dier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.47,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ja, Kuromine Asahi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.22,hallway,Text,0,0,0,,Nebežať po chodbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.22,jitsuwa-main,A,0,0,0,,Ako sa ti ten plagát páči teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.70,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Myslím, že je dobrý.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.47,jitsuwa-main,A,0,0,0,,Dobre, prerobím ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.58,jitsuwa-main,B,0,0,0,,Takže jednoducho na to pôjdem a...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.20,jitsuwa-main,C,0,0,0,,Oh, prepáč, to je len medzi nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:23.40,secrets,Text,0,0,0,,Tajomstvá
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:23.59,lies,Text,0,0,0,,Klamstvá
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:23.59,truth,Text,0,0,0,,Pravda
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:20.90,jitsuwa-internal,Text,0,0,0,,Bohužiaľ, nedokážem ani klamať, ani udržať tajomstvá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.78,jitsuwa-internal,Text,0,0,0,,Preto mi hovoria "deravý kôš".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.37,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ale, no tak,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:28.37,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,mohli by ste mi trochu viac veriť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.54,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Nuž, o dôvere toho veľa neviem,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.08,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,ale verím ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.36,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:38.43,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Nie je to zlá vec, že nedokážeš udržať tajomstvá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:39.29,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Shima...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.80,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Hej, pretože si to ty, Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:43.94,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Sakura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.66,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To hovoríte len zo srandy, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.89,jitsuwa-internal,All,0,0,0,,To bolo očividné.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.77,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, priatelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:58.78,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,Naozaj som rád, že to tak cítite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:03.11,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ale aj ja mám svoje tajomstvá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.65,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Dobre, aby sme to preložili...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:09.01,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Tajomstvo, ktoré mám od jesene prvého ročníka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:11.44,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,až do apríla druhého ročníka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.40,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Shiragami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:13.94,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:18.71,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vlastne sa mne,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:21.42,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Kurominemu Asahiovi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:28.68,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,páči toto dievča, Shiragami Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.56,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Je dosť... záhadná.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.82,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že prichádza do školy ešte pred ostatnými.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:44.32,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vždy je sama počas obeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:47.92,jitsuwa-main,D,0,0,0,,Hej, Shiragami-san, môžem si požičať tvoje poznámky?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:49.78,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Jasné.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.87,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,A bez zjavného dôvodu sa zdá,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.04,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,že chodí domov neskôr než všetci ostatní.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:59.29,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Keď nad tým tak rozmýšľam, možno je to prirodzené,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.96,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,že ja, kto nevie udržať tajomstvá,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.21,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,som priťahovaný presným opakom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.84,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Dobre, môžeš sa posadiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.12,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.59,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Čo, sakra, Asahi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.62,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ja, uh, neviem odpoveď na ďalšiu otázku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:24.15,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Upokoj sa! Ani ja ju neviem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.70,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Sakra, nám sa úplne stretli oči!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.41,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,Som zvedavý, či si všimla, že som sa pozeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.27,jitsuwa-main-top,Sensei,0,0,0,,Dobre, Kuromine, odpovieš na ďalšiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.27,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ak na to prišla...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.88,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.79,jitsuwa-main-top,Sensei,0,0,0,,Hej, Kuromine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.21,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čo budem robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.88,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Musím udržať to tajomstvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.03,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Hej, Kuromine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:41.01,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Najprv nevieš byť ticho a teraz mi neodpovedáš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.54,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Sensei, upokojte sa, prosím!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:46.59,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Koumoto-sensei, bola by som rada, keby sme pokračovali vo vyučovaní.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:50.34,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kuromine Asahi,ty sa sústredíš na vyučovanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.29,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,D-Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.14,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prepáč, predsedkyňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.39,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Dávaj si radšej pozor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.39,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,P-Prepáčte.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.90,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Takže, ďalej, pozrime sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.40,jitsuwa-main,E,0,0,0,,Takže každopádne...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.28,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To bolo zlé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.40,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.01,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Poďme sa najesť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:12.87,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Jasné.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.74,jitsuwa-main,F,0,0,0,,Shiragami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.50,jitsuwa-main,F,0,0,0,,Chceš si s nami dať obed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:21.12,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, ale mám ešte niečo na práci.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:23.04,jitsuwa-main,F,0,0,0,,Netrápte sa tým.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.28,jitsuwa-main,F,0,0,0,,Nabudúce, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:31.30,jitsuwa-main-top,All,0,0,0,,Raz, dva, tri, štyri, päť, šesť, sedem, osem...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.68,jitsuwa-main,G,0,0,0,,Tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.71,jitsuwa-main,H,0,0,0,,Au, au!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.30,jitsuwa-main,H,0,0,0,,Viac sa mi už nedá!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.68,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Pekne, pekne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.10,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,To je horúce, však, Asahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.33,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Keď o tom premýšľam,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:41.77,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Shiragami vždy vynecháva telesnú, keď je vonku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.98,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Myslel som si, že má citlivú pokožku,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.61,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,ale raz som ju videl poriadne opálenú.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:49.84,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prečo—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.98,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Na čo sa pozeráš, Eromine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.99,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Dnešok bol otrasný.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.77,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Dalo sa to čakať.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.83,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Povedal som ti, že to tak nie je.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.62,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Takže,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.71,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,kedy vyznáš svoje city Shiragami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.78,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ako—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.71,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Chcem povedať, o čom to hovoríš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.49,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Myslel si, že to skrýva.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.43,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Je jasné, že sa na ňu pozeráš.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.88,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Hej, dnes som to pokašľal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:23.69,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ale doteraz ste to nevedeli, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:27.56,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Už dlhú dobu sa mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.70,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Od minulej jesene, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.82,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,To už je chvíľa, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.61,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nemožné...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.78,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vy ste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.70,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Vedeli ste to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.54,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, že som vám to nepovedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.47,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Hanbil som sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:48.04,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nikdy som nemal v pláne jej to povedať,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.30,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,tak som o tom radšej pomlčal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.29,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Hej, no tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:55.33,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Každý má nejaké to svoje tajomstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.08,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Presne tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:59.10,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Mať tajnú lásku nie je zlé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.34,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Chalani...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.73,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Nie, vôbec to nie je dobré.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.31,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Vlastne to vôbec nebude fungovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:08.48,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Nakoniec si kôš plný dier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:10.11,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Deravý kôš!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:13.15,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Už si zabudol, Asahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:16.95,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Poníženie, ktoré si bol nútený zniesť od našej predsedkyne - nie, od Železnej slečny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:19.45,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Tragédia minulého leta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.16,jitsuwa-flashback,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kuromine Asahi, prejdem priamo k veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:28.67,jitsuwa-flashback,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ak dovolíš, bola by som rada, keby si na mňa prestal zízať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:31.46,jitsuwa-flashback,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Vôbec ma nezaujímaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:37.47,jitsuwa-flashback,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Je neracionálne pokračovať v boji, ktorý nemáš šancu vyhrať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.51,jitsuwa-flashback,Asahi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ani som sa ti nevyznal, ani nič také!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.94,jitsuwa-flashback,Shimada,0,0,0,,{\an8}Zožeňte rýchlo uterák!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.47,jitsuwa-flashback,Sakurada,0,0,0,,{\an8}Zastavte zápas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.69,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,To bolo brutálne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:44.64,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Pomyslieť si, že jeho neschopnosť udržať tajomstvo by spôsobila takúto tragédiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.81,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Porozmýšľaj nad tým, Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:51.31,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Normálne vyznanie nie je nič
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:53.69,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,v porovnaní s guľkou do chrbta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.66,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Už žiadne zásahy do chrbta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.03,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Vyznaj sa jej, než ťa odmietne!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.41,kill,Text,0,0,0,,Zabi skôr, než budeš zabitý
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.41,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vyznať sa, než budem odmietnutý!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.05,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Presne tak, Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.16,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Choď sa jej vyznať.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:10.96,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ale to nemôžem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.84,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Takže to vzdáš?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.92,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.21,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nemôžem to vzdať!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.85,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Tak choď, Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:22.14,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Navliekli sme ťa do toho, takže ťa budeme utešovať, keď bude po všetkom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.04,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Chalani...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:34.61,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Inými slovami, všetci si myslíte, že ma odmietne, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.16,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Aj tak
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:39.86,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.32,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Dobre, idem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:47.36,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Ale Shiragami-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.07,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Je pekná, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.19,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Mimo jeho ligu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.61,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Vyzerá dosť neprístupne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.93,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Nevšimli ste si to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.71,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Shiragami-san sa občas pozerala na Asahiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.09,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Myslím, že má šancu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.93,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:17.85,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:24.41,letter,Text,0,0,0,,Shiragami Youko-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.31,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Dám jej tento ľúbostný list
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.41,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,a ujdem tak rýchlo, ako viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.71,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Aj tak nemám
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.25,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,čo stratiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.38,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Takže choď, Kuromine Asahi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:50.68,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Nič nie je lepšie, ako natiahnuť si krídla v prázdnej triede.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.28,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,K-Krídla?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:22.72,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Stiahla ich!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:25.33,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,T-Tesáky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.39,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Skryla ich!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.81,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Znamená to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:39.61,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Videl si to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.02,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Videl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.96,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,U-Um, ja... Nevidel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.60,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,K-Klameš.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.59,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie, prisahám, prisahám.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:51.75,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,A dnes som ťa ani nesledoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.33,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Videl si to! Vidím ti to na tvári!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.33,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Trvá mu to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:09.55,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Som zvedavý, či to dobre dopadlo s tým vyznaním.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.78,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Možno bol už odmietnutý
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.81,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,a teraz si niekde vyplakáva oči.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.69,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Nuž, tvoje obavy nikomu nepomôžu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.97,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Poďme za ním.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:22.69,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Oh? A čo Asahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:23.94,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Vy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:25.07,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Pohanská kráľovná!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:28.61,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Prezidentka žurnalistického klubu, Akemi Mikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.95,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Ako vždy vyzeráte ako hlupáci!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:35.04,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Oh, som veľký fanúšik školských novín!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.75,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Prestaneš s tým?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.75,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Zabíja to všetku srandu, keď si to užívaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.79,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,To bolo kruté.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.84,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Prečo ste vlastne tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:46.55,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Hľadám dobrý príbeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.33,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Kde je?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.09,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Povedzte mi, kam išiel Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.73,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,A ak poviem "nie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.44,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Kto si myslíš, že som?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.04,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,"Neurob to" znamená "urob to".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.82,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,"To je tajomstvo" znamená "objav ho".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.57,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Som Akemi Mikan a to je moje motto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.22,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,To je naša pohanská kráľovná.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.96,jitsuwa-main,Sakurada,0,0,0,,Je to tvrďaska.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:11.78,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,V tom prípade...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.35,jitsuwa-main,Okada,0,0,0,,Utekajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:13.87,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Počkajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.54,jitsuwa-main,Mikan,0,0,0,,Vy chalani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:21.91,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Tajila som to, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:26.05,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Ale ja, Shiragami Youko,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.05,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,som vlastne upír.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:32.80,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Upír?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.78,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Som taká hlúpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:40.80,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Prečo som nemohla počkať, kým prídem domov, aby som si natiahla krídla?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:45.06,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Takže, uh, ty normálne hovoríš kansaiským dialektom, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:49.86,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Zvyknem sa príliš uspokojiť a ukážem tesáky, keď hovorím normálne,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:53.57,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,takže sa snažím rozprávať slušne a vyhýbať sa rozhovorom s ľuďmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:57.94,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,U-Upíri sa zmenia na prach, keď sú na slnku, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.00,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Preto na telesnej a keď chodíš do a zo školy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.61,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Nie, nezmením sa na prach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.88,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Len sa veľmi rýchlo opálim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.55,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Takže tak to bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:10.55,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Zbohom, záhadná Shiragami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.85,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Takže ty sa ma nebojíš, Kuromine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.43,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Pretože, ja, nuž...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.02,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,som upír?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.61,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie, vlastne je to celkom rozkošné.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.43,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.78,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čo to, dopekla, hovorím?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:35.45,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Um, nemýliš si to s niekým iným, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.74,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Počkať, vieš vôbec, čo je upír?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.70,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Myslela som si, že to vie každý.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:44.67,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Huh? Nevšimla si, že k nej niečo cítim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:47.55,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Je možné, že Shiragami je...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.65,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,fakt tupá?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:52.74,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Oh, prepáč. Len som si šomrala.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:56.47,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Ale chcem tým povedať...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:16:01.14,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Som rada, že si ten posledný, s kým som sa mohla porozprávať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:05.07,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Teraz, keď som bola odhalená ako upírka,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:08.73,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,musím opustiť túto školu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:13.99,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,To je podmienka, ktorú mi dal môj otec.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:18.12,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Práve som to posral?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:18.92,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:24.04,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Vážne, naozaj som si myslela, že som pripravená na to, že to raz niekto zistí.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:29.63,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Ale myslela som si, že nech to zistí hocikto, bude na smrť vystrašený.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:33.38,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Myslela som si, že sa to skončí oveľa horšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.09,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Takže, nuž...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.64,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem ti, Kuromine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:42.72,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:46.11,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ako sa môžeš takto usmievať, Shiragami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:49.36,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Chcem povedať, že toto je moja vina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.35,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Prepáč, povedala som niečo divné?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.36,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,T-To nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.37,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Nie je to tvoja vina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.54,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.80,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Shiragami nemôže teraz skončiť so školou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:07.17,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,To nechcem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:11.40,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Pokojne sa rozprávala svojím kansaiským dialektom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.74,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,a menila jeden výraz za druhým.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:19.35,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Myslím, že sa vlastne rada rozpráva s ľuďmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.32,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,A aj tak,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:23.12,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,aby si uchránila
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.60,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,toto jedno tajomstvo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.21,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Hej, to je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.74,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Pozri, som v pohode, vidíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:40.87,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Ako študentka som si užila dosť zábavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:44.33,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Dosť zábavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.68,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Takže som v pohode, vidíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:53.59,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.22,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To nemôžem dovoliť!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.22,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Kuromine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:02.51,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Pozri, nechcem, aby si teraz len tak opustila školu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.27,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,O čom to hovorím?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:08.02,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Chcem povedať, um, vieš...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.23,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To je ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.98,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Môžeš udržať v tajnosti, že bolo tvoje tajomstvo prezradené.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.52,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Hej. To je ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.40,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,A nebudeš musieť odísť zo školy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:20.54,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ja, nuž... Očividne sa ma dá ľahko prečítať.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:23.91,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ľudia o mne hovoria, že som zlý klamár a neviem udržať tajomstvá.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.55,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ale toto jedno...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.16,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Len toto jedno tajomstvo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:30.54,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prisahám, že za všetkých okolností udržím to tajomstvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.55,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Takže, Shiragami Youko-san, prosím...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.00,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Prosím...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.88,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Buďme priatelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.30,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:43.92,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Priatelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.94,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čo, dopekla, to robím?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.03,jitsuwa-flashback,,0,0,0,,Poď na to, deravý kôš.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.16,jitsuwa-flashback,,0,0,0,,Tu máš!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.69,jitsuwa-flashback,,0,0,0,,Nič som necítil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.66,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Priatelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:10.33,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Uh, to je... chcem povedať...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.85,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Povedal som niečo divné?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.22,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Kuromine-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.13,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,nuž...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.14,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Ak som dosť dobrá,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.86,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,veľmi rada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:39.36,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,A tak ja, Kuromine Asahi,deravý kôš, ktorý nevie klamať ani udržať tajomstvá,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:43.13,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,teraz mám jedno tajomstvo, ktoré určite musím udržať.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.70,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,Preklad a časovanie:\NDashio
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:53.70,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,Korekcia:\NHaany
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:57.70,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,Titulky od GAW-Subs\Nwww.gawsubs.com\N2015
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:20.17,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Musíš čakať do takejto neskorej hodiny, aby si mohla ísť domov, hej?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:25.44,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Nuž, nemôžem prísť každý deň do školy opálená.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:27.09,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To je pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:32.45,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Keď už o tom hovoríme, nikdy si si nevšimol, že som upír, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:35.64,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie, zistil som to až dnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:39.65,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Takže to {\i1}ja{\i0} som bola až príliš rozpačitá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:40.52,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Kvôli čomu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:45.86,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Nuž, mala som pocit, že sa na mňa dosť pozeráš.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:52.44,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Takže som si myslela, že si si možno všimol, že som upírka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:55.66,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,P-Povedzme, že je to tajomstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.94,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,T-Tajomstvo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.96,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Trčia mi chlpy z nosa alebo niečo také?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:02.67,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.90,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Som rada.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:11.27,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Povedal si, že máš ešte iné tajomstvá, takže si ma vystrašil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:12.96,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:18.50,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Hej, mal som ešte iné tajomstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:23.20,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Toto tajomstvo si zoberiem so sebou do hrobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:25.44,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,aby som ochránil Shiragami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:28.57,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Počuj, Shiragami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:33.41,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Jedného dňa ti moje tajomstvo prezradím.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:36.19,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vypočuj si ma, keď príde ten čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:37.38,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,O čom to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:40.84,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Je to trochu strašidelné, keď z toho robíš takú vedu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:53.03,jitsuwa-main,A,0,0,0,,Komunikačný systém je online.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.59,0:22:57.28,jitsuwa-main,B,0,0,0,,Tu je kód 138.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:22:59.27,jitsuwa-main,B,0,0,0,,Operácia pokračuje bez problémov.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:01.60,jitsuwa-main,B,0,0,0,,Vraciam sa k štandardným povinnostiam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:05.94,jitsuwa-main,B,0,0,0,,Známky života na jednej hodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.02,0:23:12.99,jitsuwa-main,B,0,0,0,,To sú...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.99,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Kuromine Asahi a Shiragami Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:18.86,jitsuwa-main,B,0,0,0,,Prečo sú tam tak neskoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:24.42,quiz,Text,0,0,0,,Vlastne som kvíz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:24.42,guess,Text,0,0,0,,Môžeš hádať?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:23.50,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Čas na: Vlastne som kvíz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:24.42,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prečo teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:26.24,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Čia je to silueta?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:27.36,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Neodpovedáš mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:28.36,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nejaká nápoveda?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:31.53,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Scenár hovorí, že je to láska Kuromine-kuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:33.54,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Zastavte ten kvíz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:34.88,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Čo to robíš, Kuromine-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.31,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Nevidím, keď tam máš ruku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:38.05,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To nemusíš vidieť!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:39.33,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Dávam preč tvoju ruku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:41.06,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nepozeraj sa, Shiragami!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.74,jitsuwa-main,Shimada,0,0,0,,Nevykladaj si to zle, Eromine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.74,0:23:45.07,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čo, dopekla, Shima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:48.04,jitsuwa-main,Shiragami,0,0,0,,Ty máš naozaj blízko k svojim kamošom, huh, Kuromine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:50.95,jitsuwa-next_ep,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,1)}Nabudúce:\N"Udržím toto tajomstvo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:50.68,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Môžeme tento segment už nerobiť?
